Paper: hep-th/9904074

Date: 1999-04-09

Title: Anomaly induced effective actions and Hawking radiation

Authors: Roberto Balbinot, Alessandro Fabbri and Ilya Shapiro

Comments: 4 pages, revtek

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev.Lett. 83 (1999) 1494-1497

The quantum stress tensor in the Unruh state for a conformal scalarpropagating in a 4D Schwarzschild black hole spacetime is reconstructed in itsleading behaviour at infinity and near the horizon by means of an effectiveaction derived by functionally integrating the trace anomaly.